OL,4,G2030FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,5,     GIn 1944, American forces launched
OL,6,     Ga final push to retake the
OL,7,     GPhilippines after two years of
OL,8,     GJapanese occupation.
OL,9,G2100FWWII Battles in Colour
OL,10,     GJuly 1943. The German advance has
OL,11,     Gstalled, but Hitler is convinced
OL,12,     Ghis new generation of tanks will
OL,13,     Gput the Reich back on the path to
OL,14,     Gdomination. His target: the
OL,15,     GSoviet town of Kursk.
OL,16,G2200FWWII Battles in Colour
OL,17,     GIn late 1944, Allied confidence
OL,18,     Gwas high. But the war was about
OL,19,     Gto take a dramatic turn,
OL,20,     Gresulting in the U.S. army's
OL,21,     Glargest and bloodiest conflict of
OL,22,     GWWII: The Battle of the Bulge.
